introduction: As a Native of New York City and trained by noteable coaches such as Anthony Abeson, and Lynn Lipton, Jason Delfino has been a performer for over 25 years with experiences on Broadway, Film & Television,Voice Overs Both in The U.S. and China.  Noteable appearances include: MTV, FUSE, and TRU TV. Most Recently, Jason will be doing voice overs for a character yet to be named for "Harry Potter Magic Awakend" online game.
